title: Location & Luxury in Harmony here with this 1 bedroom home
posting_body: ['Upscale living!', 'Plenty of opportunities to relax, unwind, and stay engaged with the community.', 'Lounge at the resort-style rooftop pool, where you can get some sun on the tanning ledge or flood your stress away with a refreshing swim.', 'Outdoor kitchens and grills offer a wonderful place to hang out with neighbors and enjoy a meal as you take in the sunny weather.', 'When you want to be active, head over to the fully equipped fitness center and work out with your favorite Peloton instructor on our bikes.', 'If you have guests over, take advantage of the media room and serving kitchen, which has all the space you need to create a gourmet meal for a larger crowd.', 'As a pet-friendly community, we also have a pet park on-site with a dog run, giving your pup lots of open space to burn off energy.', 'And work from home is a breeze with High-Speed Internet & 24hr.', 'Emergency maintenance, when needed.', 'Where?', 'A TRENDY AUSTIN NEIGHBORHOOD', 'Located in the heart of Austin’s acclaimed Burnet Road corridor, residents have easy access to some of the city’s most famous restaurants and bakeries—many within walking distance.', 'Pinthouse Pizza is a favorite place to meet up with friends after work, while The Peached Tortilla is known for delicious Asian-Southern American fusion.', 'Walk up the street for a healthy meal at Honest Mary’s or settle in for an upscale Italian dinner at Gusto’s.', 'On lazy mornings, head to Gourdough’s Donuts for creative takes on brunch.', 'With our great location near the North Loop, you’ll always have something new and fun to explore in the Brentwood neighborhood.', 'To round out your experience, Downtown Austin is just 4.2 miles away, home to popular food trucks and restaurants, as well as great entertainment.', 'Austin also has plenty of affordable public transportation options, making your commute around town a breeze.', 'Get it!', 'This Locator gives generous money back rebates of $50-$250.00!', 'Ask how to get yours!', 'Text 2I0-355-7852', 'Christena Barry - Award Winning Locator & Realtor', 'Spirit Real Estate Group', 'ID:  99', '*Pics show general property, not necessarily particular unit.', '*Prices, availability, & specials subject to change.']
